136
00:07:21,848 --> 00:07:26,831
spend more time on the overall frame and less on the individual quality of an asset because

137
00:07:26,831 --> 00:07:31,514
we know that person is moving very quickly through the scene. And also photorealism,

138
00:07:31,514 --> 00:07:35,796
the nice thing about it is that it's a clear style choice. We know what we're trying to hit.

139
00:07:36,166 --> 00:07:37,627
