00:18:56,561 --> 00:19:01,343
These are all the things both in our game and when you're painting or doing anything

352
00:19:01,343 --> 00:19:01,883
that add up.

353
00:19:02,142 --> 00:19:08,406
to being a beautifully lit scene that looks photorealistic to you.

