00:34:54,888 --> 00:34:57,489
as you're driving around the track, there's the hotel again,

660
00:34:57,489 --> 00:35:00,350
that that is what you're gonna see the majority of the time,

661
00:35:00,350 --> 00:35:02,351
and that's what's gonna have your visual impression.

662
00:35:02,709 --> 00:35:06,893
And we let the other stuff just kind of bleed off into the, into the distance.

663
00:35:06,893 --> 00:35:20,286
This is an example from Rio. This is basically what I was talking about before where if we know that this is on at the end of a long straightaway we built this iconic moment this shot of Sugarloaf Mountain, and we know that we have your

